data.description: Back on Market due to NO FAULT of the home - Buyer got cold feet before Inspection was completed. Rare find in town!! Almost 1/3 acre lot, NO HOA, and NO METRO TAXES!! Room for RV Parking on the side of the home! This 3 Bedroom, 2 Bathroom home has been lovingly cared for over the years and is waiting for you to call it your own. Basement has been finished with a remodeled bathroom, and it could easily be converted for another bedroom or 2! All Appliances stay! All the big-ticket updates have been done - Bathrooms have been remodeled, Newer flooring on the main level, Newer windows, Newer blinds, Newer kitchen appliances are top of the line, Newer Roof AND Exterior walls were all recently insulated with high quality insulation! HUGE backyard feels like your own personal park! Heated and Insulated oversized garage. Finished basement includes family room with fireplace and lots of room for storage! All appliances stay! 1 Year Home Warranty Included. Priced to Sell! Quick close possible.
